SUMMARY:Aniketh Mikkilineni [@axm]
DESCRIPTION:<2026-04-29 Wed 13:00-14:30>\n• ☐ HB: purchase items\n  1. ☐ +P
 FTE+ Nylon tubing\, 40ft or 12m min\n  2. ☐ Flowmeters\, 2x\n  3. ☐ +Adapt
 ers from tubing to 8mm barb flowmeter\, 2x min+\n  4. ☐ T or Y-Connectors\
 , 2x min\n  5. ☐ Needle valve\n• ☑ HB: contact Glenda about mixing gases a
 nd running tubing.\n• ☑ HB: measure distance to determine length of 1/4 in
  PFTE tubing.\n  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
 ━━\n   Distance\, ft  Description\n  ─────────────────────────────────────
 ──────────────────────\n              2  Valve to counter edge\n          
     6  From valve going up to ceiling support\n             18  Across cei
 ling support\n              6  From ceiling support down to counter height
 \n              8  From support across to UV/vis spec\n  ─────────────────
 ──────────────────────────────────────────\n             40  Total\n  ━━━━
 ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
CATEGORIES:@axm,BRG
SEQUENCE:1
PRIORITY:5
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
